text: Erin Wasson (born January 20, 1982) is an American model, actress and designer. She has had roles in several movies. She was also on the covers of several fashion magazines, including Vogue, Esquire and Elle. She walked international runways for fashion designers. Wasson was born in Irving, Texas.
